### Ruby Navigation

- **Base class**: Components inherit from [app/components/primer/component.rb](mdc:app/components/primer/component.rb). It mixes in helpers, status DSL, and audited DSL.
- **Rails engine**: Mounts and initializers live in [lib/primer/view_components/engine.rb](mdc:lib/primer/view_components/engine.rb).
- **Gem namespace**: Start at [lib/primer/view_components.rb](mdc:lib/primer/view_components.rb) for requires and configuration.
- **Statuses and constants**: [lib/primer/view_components/statuses.rb](mdc:lib/primer/view_components/statuses.rb), [lib/primer/view_components/constants.rb](mdc:lib/primer/view_components/constants.rb).
- **Static generation**: Entrypoint [lib/primer/static.rb](mdc:lib/primer/static.rb) and generators in `lib/primer/static/*` create JSON under `static/`.

Conventions:
- Component class file: `app/components/primer/<component>.rb`
- Template: `app/components/primer/<component>.html.erb`
- Styles: `app/components/primer/<component>.pcss`
- Preview: `previews/primer/<component>_preview.rb` with example ERB under `previews/primer/**`.

Testing:
- Component tests in `test/components/**` and lib tests in `test/lib/**`.
- System and accessibility tests live under `test/system/**` and [test/accessibility_test.rb](mdc:test/accessibility_test.rb).
